      <title>澳大利亚希望随着葡萄酒销量增长与中国葡萄酒贸易复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/australia-hopeful-wine-trade-with-china-to-recover-as-sales-jump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚乐观地认为，在惩罚性关税结束后，该国与中国的葡萄酒贸易销量将大幅增长，并全面恢复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/australia-hopeful-wine-trade-with-china-to-recover-as-sales-jump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 03:58:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界银行称生活成本飙升将抑制缅甸经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/soaring-living-costs-to-curb-myanmar-s-growth-world-bank-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界银行周三在一份新报告中表示，由于食品和燃料成本高昂、本币贬值以及美元短缺拖累经济，缅甸本财年经济增长可能维持疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/soaring-living-costs-to-curb-myanmar-s-growth-world-bank-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 03:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国部长警告称，勒庞当选将引发类似“桁架式”的债务危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/le-maire-warns-of-french-debt-crisis-if-le-pen-s-party-wins-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国财政部长布鲁诺·勒梅尔警告称，如果极右翼领导人玛丽娜·勒庞赢得本月底举行的立法选举并实施其经济计划，法国将陷入与两年前英国类似的债务危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/le-maire-warns-of-french-debt-crisis-if-le-pen-s-party-wins-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 20:35:11 GMT</pubDate>
